title: "This team"
body:
I respond, {{champion:150}}  "We all suck." (I was doing poorly, along with every other member of our team excluding Nami)

{{champion:63}}  "No, just you and Lee." (2/4 Brand)
{{champion:150}} "Your MMR is about the same as mine."
{{champion:63}} "Just you and Lee suck."
{{champion:150}} "Tell me, then, why your MMR isn't higher."
{{champion:63}} *No response*

That's what I thought.
